FEATURES
========
[x] Solid mode
  [x] Pulse brightness option
[ ] Gradient mode
  [ ] Pulse brightness option
  [ ] Rotate option (gradient moves along strip, last colour blends back to first)
[ ] Sequence mode - list of colours, show each for X seconds, blend to next, loop

